<rml>
<head>
	<title>Goal Quest</title>
	<link type="text/rcss" href="GoalQuestWidget.rcss"/>
</head>
<body>
	<div id="quest-root">
		<div id="quest-panel">
			<div class="quest-badge">ENDING</div>
			<div class="quest-title">탈출!</div>
			<div class="quest-body">탈출구를 찾아 이 세계를 탈출하세요.</div>
			<button id="goal-quest-ok-button" class="quest-button">Okay</button>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</rml>
